We need to be able to create clusters based on:

* issues
* objections
* feature requests
* features

we can base all of these on tags. 

Represent these as: 

```
table tag_group (
  id bigint;
  created_at; 
  created_by;
  name text;
  description text; 
  classification_instructions text;
  organization_id bigint;
  is_hierarchical boolean;
  is_multi_select boolean;
}

table tag_group_member {
  id bigint;
  created_at; 
  created_by;
  tag_group_id bigint;
  tag_id bigint;
}

table tag_group_member_relationship {
  id bigint;
  created_at; 
  created_by;
  parent_tag_id bigint;
  child_tag_id bigint;
}
```

